<br>
if you don't know it yet :<br>
1/ summon earth pet<br>
2/ send pet. He roots mob, then goes to fight.<br>
3/ sit and wait for pet to be low (here is the problem : you must learn what 'low' is for each mob)<br>
4/ get up, cast new pet<br>
5/ open pet window (or type '/pet get lost' without hitting the enter key)<br>
6/ when casting is on the last half blue, clic on the 'go away' button or hit enter.<br>
7/ old pet desapears, new one is ready.<br>
8/ goto 2/<br>
<br>
...<br>
