Earth pet has allways been my favorite solo pet.<br>
...<br>
but I think learning how to chain pet is a MUST for a mage. Later on you will meet mobs that you cannot solo if you don't chain.<br>
Chaining is also usefull with a mage group !<br>
...<br>
