The earth root is a pet killer too many times.  Thy this....<br>
<br>
<br>
Use Air/fire/water pull with your highest DD to get argo. Turn off pet taunt and using Jboots or sow potion reverse kite the mob with pet beating on it. Running in a circle works best. Once pet have argo chain DD till you get argo again and repeat.<br>
